title: Mick Fleetwood Sips George T. Stagg, Reveals He Misses Hugs  While Isolated, And Talks About Bandmates Peter Green And Neil Finn
itunes:title: Mick Fleetwood Sips George T. Stagg, Reveals He Misses Hugs  While Isolated, And Talks About Bandmates Peter Green And Neil Finn
description:
When the great Mick Fleetwood sips some good whiskey with Fred Minnick over Zoom, the iconic Fleetwood Mac drummer digs deep into his personal life and shares details of his life he never has before. Along the way, he talks olfactory, missing hugs and restaurants during the pandemic and Peter Green, whom he credits for founding Fleetwood Mac.
